      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained. The engine starts reliably and runs strong, providing a consistent driving experience, while the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. Inside, the cabin is clean with only minor signs of wear consistent with regular use. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, though a few small stone chips or light surface scratches may be found upon close inspection. Overall, this is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without any immediate mechanical needs.",
