    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, drivable option for those who prioritize utility over aesthetics. While the powertrain remains operational and the car drives fine, there are visible signs of wear, including several scratches on the exterior paint and some fading on the interior seats. It has been used regularly and may require minor mechanical repairs or servicing soon to maintain its current performance level. This is a straightforward, honest car for someone looking for a budget-friendly transport option.",
