    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system to deliver exceptional throttle response, paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement and a factory M-Variable Lock limited-slip differential. Maintenance is current, including a recent valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization and suspension geometry remain dialed for a precise, analog driving experience. A well-maintained example of M-division's peak engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
