    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish that catches the light beautifully, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper\u2014typical of careful city driving. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring premium leather seating that remains supple; there is only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the touchscreen infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. The engine pulls smoothly with no hesitation, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes were recently inspected with plenty of life remaining. It has been serviced regularly at 5,000-mile intervals, and I have the records to prove it. This is a solid, reliable, and handsome vehicle that is ready for its next owner to drive home today with total confidence.",
